00:45:51.240 --> 00:45:54.990 align:middle line:84%
>> What does an anti-cancer
diet look like in your office?

00:45:54.990 --> 00:45:57.490 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, we teach our patients--

00:45:57.490 --> 00:46:00.690 align:middle line:84%
I'm not the nutritionist,
but I do instruct patients.

00:46:00.690 --> 00:46:04.920 align:middle line:10%
First of all, you
have to eat foods--

00:46:04.920 --> 00:46:07.650 align:middle line:10%
mostly vegetables.

00:46:07.650 --> 00:46:09.330 align:middle line:10%
I don't care if they
eat fruits, but you

00:46:09.330 --> 00:46:12.040 align:middle line:10%
have to eat a low sugar diet
because cancer feeds off

00:46:12.040 --> 00:46:12.840 align:middle line:10%
of sugar.

00:46:12.840 --> 00:46:16.080 align:middle line:84%
Dr. Otto Warburg
won a Nobel Prize.

00:46:16.080 --> 00:46:21.600 align:middle line:84%
He said that cancer cells
thrive in a fermentative energy

00:46:21.600 --> 00:46:24.990 align:middle line:90%
source, which is sugar.

00:46:24.990 --> 00:46:27.210 align:middle line:84%
On the cancer cells, the
receptor sites for sugar,

00:46:27.210 --> 00:46:28.980 align:middle line:90%
that's how we do a PET scan.

00:46:28.980 --> 00:46:31.110 align:middle line:84%
When you give a
PET scan, you give

00:46:31.110 --> 00:46:34.950 align:middle line:84%
it radiotrace glucose and
the cancer cells light up

00:46:34.950 --> 00:46:35.970 align:middle line:90%
or they don't light up.

00:46:35.970 --> 00:46:38.430 align:middle line:84%
And they light up because
they're eating the sugar

00:46:38.430 --> 00:46:40.210 align:middle line:90%
or they don't.

00:46:40.210 --> 00:46:42.360 align:middle line:84%
So you've got to get
people off sugar.

00:46:42.360 --> 00:46:44.040 align:middle line:90%
People are addicted to sugar.

00:46:44.040 --> 00:46:48.690 align:middle line:84%
Sugar is a poison, it's a
toxin, and it paralyzes the cell

00:46:48.690 --> 00:46:50.210 align:middle line:90%
from doing their job.

00:46:50.210 --> 00:46:52.085 align:middle line:84%
We have this blood test
called the hemoglobin

00:46:52.085 --> 00:46:56.550 align:middle line:84%
A1c, which is a reflection of
your blood sugar over 90 days.

00:46:56.550 --> 00:46:58.830 align:middle line:90%
It is an aging marker.

00:46:58.830 --> 00:47:03.340 align:middle line:84%
Your body has what they call
glycosylation taking place.

00:47:03.340 --> 00:47:06.430 align:middle line:84%
We know that at
a certain number,

00:47:06.430 --> 00:47:09.240 align:middle line:84%
with the electron
microscopy Johns Hopkins

00:47:09.240 --> 00:47:12.630 align:middle line:84%
has written on this,
that the cells change

00:47:12.630 --> 00:47:15.720 align:middle line:84%
after a hemoglobin
A1c greater than 5.0,

00:47:15.720 --> 00:47:18.210 align:middle line:90%
which is considered ideal.

00:47:18.210 --> 00:47:20.070 align:middle line:90%
So you have to get off sugar.

00:47:20.070 --> 00:47:22.160 align:middle line:90%
I don't care how you slice it.

00:47:22.160 --> 00:47:24.090 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, there are people
that can eat sugar

00:47:24.090 --> 00:47:26.940 align:middle line:84%
and they have
great blood sugars.

00:47:26.940 --> 00:47:30.430 align:middle line:84%
Luckily, they're blessed,
but most people are not.

00:47:30.430 --> 00:47:33.300 align:middle line:84%
I mean, if you look
at the statistics, 70,

00:47:33.300 --> 00:47:35.640 align:middle line:84%
80 million people
are pre-diabetic.

00:47:35.640 --> 00:47:38.860 align:middle line:84%
So that means they're already
very increased risk of cancer.

00:47:38.860 --> 00:47:40.080 align:middle line:90%
Then you have the diabetics.

00:47:40.080 --> 00:47:41.490 align:middle line:84%
Then if you look
at children, one

00:47:41.490 --> 00:47:46.410 align:middle line:84%
in three children after the
year 2000 have diabetes.

00:47:46.410 --> 00:47:49.530 align:middle line:84%
The complications of
diabetes are everything.

00:47:49.530 --> 00:47:52.980 align:middle line:84%
Your eyes, your circulation,
your heart, your immune system,

00:47:52.980 --> 00:47:54.600 align:middle line:90%
everything is nonfunctional.

00:47:54.600 --> 00:47:56.649 align:middle line:90%
Amputation of limbs.

00:47:56.649 --> 00:47:59.190 align:middle line:84%
Probably that's the number one
reason for amputation of limbs

00:47:59.190 --> 00:48:00.382 align:middle line:90%
is from high blood sugar.

00:48:00.382 --> 00:48:02.340 align:middle line:84%
So you've got to get off
sugar, and then you've

00:48:02.340 --> 00:48:05.034 align:middle line:84%
got to get off the things
that turn into sugar.

00:48:05.034 --> 00:48:06.450 align:middle line:84%
So the things that
turn into sugar

00:48:06.450 --> 00:48:08.340 align:middle line:84%
are bread, rice,
pasta, and potatoes.

00:48:08.340 --> 00:48:10.110 align:middle line:90%
