>> Clean.

00:49:38.860 --> 00:49:41.290 align:middle line:10%
As clean as possible, meaning
that it should be organic,

00:49:41.290 --> 00:49:43.092 align:middle line:10%
range fed.

00:49:43.092 --> 00:49:45.300 align:middle line:84%
In my book, "The Nine Steps
