00:49:46.900 --> 00:49:48.400 align:middle line:84%
And people have
asked me many times,

00:49:48.400 --> 00:49:51.040 align:middle line:84%
when are you going to write
a more detailed book on food?

00:49:51.040 --> 00:49:53.350 align:middle line:84%
