00:49:54.850 --> 00:49:55.070 align:middle line:90%
Why?

00:49:55.070 --> 00:49:56.920 align:middle line:84%
Because I want people to
become empowered rather than

00:49:56.920 --> 00:49:58.460 align:middle line:90%
becoming dependent on a book.

00:49:58.460 --> 00:50:01.040 align:middle line:84%
So it's a very,
very simple rule.

00:50:01.040 --> 00:50:06.050 align:middle line:84%
G stands for God,
M stands for man.

00:50:06.050 --> 00:50:07.640 align:middle line:90%
If God made it, it's good.

00:50:07.640 --> 00:50:09.350 align:middle line:90%
If man made it, it's madness.

00:50:09.350 --> 00:50:11.220 align:middle line:90%
Simply follow that rule.

00:50:11.220 --> 00:50:15.970 align:middle line:84%
So if it's butter and doctor
said don't eat butter,

00:50:15.970 --> 00:50:17.680 align:middle line:90%
it's fat, this, that--

00:50:17.680 --> 00:50:19.130 align:middle line:84%
it's not man made,
it's God made.

00:50:19.130 --> 00:50:19.930 align:middle line:90%
Eat it.

00:50:19.930 --> 00:50:21.250 align:middle line:84%
If it's margarine,
it's man made.

00:50:21.250 --> 00:50:22.749 align:middle line:84%
Use it for lubrication
in your car's

00:50:22.749 --> 00:50:25.030 align:middle line:84%
axle, but don't use
it for anything else.

00:50:25.030 --> 00:50:27.370 align:middle line:90%
So that's my general rule.

00:50:27.370 --> 00:50:30.690 align:middle line:84%
High protein,
lower carbohydrates

00:50:30.690 --> 00:50:33.540 align:middle line:84%
because protein is part of how
the body regenerates itself,

00:50:33.540 --> 00:50:35.640 align:middle line:90%
whereas carbohydrates are fuel.

00:50:35.640 --> 00:50:38.610 align:middle line:84%
We have too much fuel
in our diet nowadays.

00:50:38.610 --> 00:50:41.040 align:middle line:84%
We needed more fuel
when we were more back

00:50:41.040 --> 00:50:42.780 align:middle line:84%
in a paleolithic
ancestry, but that's

00:50:42.780 --> 00:50:45.120 align:middle line:90%
because we had to hunt our food.

00:50:45.120 --> 00:50:46.920 align:middle line:84%
We don't hunt our
hamburgers now,

00:50:46.920 --> 00:50:49.480 align:middle line:84%
and so we don't really
need as much fuel anymore.

00:50:49.480 --> 00:50:54.030 align:middle line:84%
So you need more of a
rebuilder protein component

00:50:54.030 --> 00:50:56.970 align:middle line:84%
and you need less of the
carbohydrate fuel component.

00:50:56.970 --> 00:50:59.970 align:middle line:84%
So my general rule
is man made, madness.

00:50:59.970 --> 00:51:01.410 align:middle line:90%
God made, good.

00:51:01.410 --> 00:51:04.350 align:middle line:84%
Eat as clean as you can, meaning
organic, range fed, et cetera.

00:51:04.350 --> 00:51:05.310 align:middle line:90%
Fruits, vegetables.

00:51:05.310 --> 00:51:10.020 align:middle line:84%
If you're going to eat meat,
then eat range fed meat.

00:51:10.020 --> 00:51:12.100 align:middle line:90%
And eat as healthy as possible.

00:51:12.100 --> 00:51:12.900 align:middle line:90%
And people know.

