01:02:09.289 --> 01:02:11.580 align:middle line:84%
And my wife and I, it just
kind of threw us for a loop.

01:02:11.580 --> 01:02:12.740 align:middle line:84%
Because when you have
one of your siblings

01:02:12.740 --> 01:02:14.281 align:middle line:84%
